{ lib, buildRosPackage, fetchurl, ament-cmake, ament-lint-auto, ament-lint-common, geometry-msgs, lifecycle-msgs, rclcpp, rclcpp-components, rclcpp-lifecycle, sensor-msgs, std-srvs }:
